        "question_adqrYK": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Is the bottle leak-proof?",
            "answer": "<p>Yes! The bottle is fully sealed when closed, so you can toss it in your bag, backpack, or car without worrying about spills. Both the water and treat compartments are leak-resistant by design.</p>"
          }
        },
        "question_TDP7NK": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Is it safe for my pet?",
            "answer": "<p>Absolutely. The bottle is made from BPA-free, food-grade, pet-safe materials — gentle on your furry friend and built to last. It's just like the materials used in human water bottles, so totally safe for daily use.</p>"
          }
        },
        "question_hPGXCN": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Will it work for both dogs and cats?",
            "answer": "<p>Yes! The bottle is designed for pets of all sizes — from tiny kittens to large dogs. The built-in folding bowl adjusts so any pet can drink comfortably, and the compact size makes it easy to carry no matter your pet's size.</p>"
          }
        },
        "question_7Rxwez": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "How do I clean it?",
            "answer": "<p>Super easy! Just rinse both compartments with warm water and mild soap, then let them air dry. We recommend cleaning after each long outing to keep everything fresh and hygienic for your pet.</p>"
          }
        },
        "question_Pzgd7t": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "How much water does it hold?",
            "answer": "<p>The water compartment holds approximately 350ml — perfect for medium-length walks, hikes, or daily outings. The separate treat section keeps treats fresh and ready for training or rewards along the way.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
